Father, we love you.

00:39:56.960 --> 00:39:58.380
We thank you so much for loving us.

00:39:58.380 --> 00:40:00.720
Thank you for the passage of Scripture that is before us.

00:40:00.720 --> 00:40:04.000
this evening, we thank you for the opportunity

00:40:04.000 --> 00:40:07.200
to have a Bible and to read and understand.

00:40:07.200 --> 00:40:09.800
And I pray, God, that you'd give us a mind to understand,

00:40:09.800 --> 00:40:11.080
give us a heart to understand.

00:40:11.080 --> 00:40:13.200
Lord, give us a burden.

00:40:13.200 --> 00:40:15.560
Those of us that have been saved by the blood of Christ,

00:40:15.560 --> 00:40:18.640
give us a burden to reach the lost around us.

00:40:18.640 --> 00:40:21.200
I pray that in the moment of invitation that you'd work,

00:40:21.200 --> 00:40:24.200
I pray that we'd be doers of the word and not hearers only.

00:40:24.200 --> 00:40:25.760
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:40:25.760 --> 00:40:26.740
Would you stand with me?

00:40:26.740 --> 00:40:28.520
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

00:40:28.520 --> 00:40:30.420
Kimberly's gonna play quietly on the piano

00:40:30.420 --> 00:40:32.560
and as she does, the altar is open.

